Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:37.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96034,97744}– Bye!\N– No breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:39.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97744,99120}No, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:40.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99704,100997}I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:49.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106252,109422}That hurts!\NWatch where you're driving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:109422,112383}– I'm sorry.\N– Oh, really! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113301,114844}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:59.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118306,119891}Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:01.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120725,121934}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:10.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126939,130318}Please accept our deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131486,133905}I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136866,139118}Master Ryutaro, she forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:22.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139827,142330}I'm almost positive\Nit's a St. Paulia School hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143665,144832}I've found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.83,saint tail default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:146709,150838}Meimi is Engaged\Nto a Multi-millionaire's Son!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:41.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157095,161808}– Don't be depressed about being tardy.\N– Sister's lecture is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:43.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161808,163601}Good, if that's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.06,0:02:47.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164060,167897}It might be the Board Chairman\Nwho will give you a lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:51.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167897,171109}You're kidding!\NI was only late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:54.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171109,174570}Meimi! Please come\Nto the Chairman's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174862,176322}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:04.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181577,184038}Don't you think\Nsomething's strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:05.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184038,185915}Oh, it's you, Saruwatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185915,188042}The name's Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188042,189836}What's so strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:14.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189836,194465}Do you think you'd be called to\Nthe Chairman's office for being tardy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194465,195550}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195550,198428}I think this is gonna be a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202181,204183}Meimi, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204183,205435}Yes, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206561,209564}I'm very sorry!\NI was tardy because a car—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:33.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209564,213901}She's the one! No mistake!\NShe's the one I've been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214444,215820}You're—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:40.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216154,220616}I'm very sorry about this morning.\NMy name is Ryutaro Tomikoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:46.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221367,226038}This morning you dropped your hat.\NThis gentleman came to return it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:48.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226038,228499}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:56.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230084,236048}And also it's very sudden, but Mr. Tomikoji\Nrequests that he be given the chance to date you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236048,238092}Date? With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:02.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238634,242263}This meeting is a God-given destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:242263,244891}Love at first sight\Nis what you'd call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:08.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244891,248019}{\i1}It's all so sudden. Besides…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:248019,250104}Miss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:13.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250104,253775}If you accept, we shall\Nforget the tardy incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:17.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254233,257945}Well, he's a most\Ncourteous young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:21.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257945,261449}To go out of his way for permission\Nto date one of our students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261449,262742}You're correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263367,266454}Everyone tells me so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268956,270917}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271209,272835}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:37.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272835,277632}I was sure you'd give that reply.\NWell, it's time we leave for our date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:42.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278216,282386}Please take good care\Nof our Meimi. And now…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:45.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282386,285848}Regarding the contribution, I will\Nhave a company employee prepare it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:48.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287892,288976}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288976,291813}{\i1}Contribution? I've been sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292939,294732}Then we'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294732,297235}Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.23,saint tail sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:295983,297235}{\fad(250,0)}Gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301239,303115}Scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306494,307703}It's a scoop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310915,314544}A simple park like this\Ncan be quite refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314544,317380}I couldn't think of\Nanywhere for a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317380,320174}I think your pureness is so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:25.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322009,325263}{\i1}That's it! I should ask him\Nfor the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325263,328140}{\i1}Then he'd be convinced\Nto forget this date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328558,329684}I've thought of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329684,331727}Wherever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:36.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331727,336440}I'd like to eat at Tetsujin-tei\Nand go to a musical at Bayside Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336440,338734}Let's not forget Wonderland Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338734,341070}Okay. Let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351247,353791}What a long line!\NMaybe we should—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:57.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353791,357044}Meimi, what's the matter?\NThe entrance is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357545,360006}But we've got to stand in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363926,367013}We came in without standing in line.\NAre you sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:11.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367763,371601}Mother is sponsor of this restaurant\Nso we can come in anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:15.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371601,375479}I see. Ryutaro, your mother\Nis quite a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:20.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375980,380985}Yes. After Father's death, she's been\Nrunning the company by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:23.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380985,383487}But she does too much\Nwhen it comes to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:28.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383487,388451}Like deciding my fiancée.\NI'd like to decide on my own fiancée.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:30.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388910,390286}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:33.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390286,393331}Well, the musical is next, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:38.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393331,398002}Yes. Could you possibly be sponsors\Nof the Bayside Hall as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398920,401088}You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:44.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401088,404967}But Mother has special reserved seats\Nso there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406677,410306}{\i1}This guy has no idea\Nwhat standing in line is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410306,411682}Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411682,412975}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:56.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413309,416520}My parents will be worried\Nif I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416520,417521}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:02.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417521,422777}Next time, we'll get permission\Nfrom your parents and enjoy our date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422777,424570}I'll take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:424570,427865}Don't worry. I can get home\Nby myself. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428574,431827}Meimi! You're shy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:19.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435456,439794}This is the fourth day. No matter\Nwhat Sister says, I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:22.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440086,442546}Meimi, don't be such a spoilsport!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:26.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442546,446467}She's right. You get to go\Nto all the popular places.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:31.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446467,451013}It's God's teachings. That's what you\Nget for accepting a date so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:35.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451597,455810}Oh, Seira. I'm leaving from\Nthe back gate so he won't catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455810,457687}I'm leaving the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:47.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463609,467905}Young lady, we've been waiting\Nfor you. Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:50.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469198,470408}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474412,477373}Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478416,481669}If you're okay with it,\NI'd be glad to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:07.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481669,487800}Someone switched the heirloom necklace\Nmy mother left me with a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491512,494640}– This is it.\N– What? This shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495391,497643}Mother is the sponsor\Nof this boutique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497935,500396}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500396,503107}I'd like to select something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:25.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503107,505192}You don't have to buy me clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:29.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505192,509363}You're meeting my mother,\Nso please be conscious of your dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.78,0:08:30.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509780,510865}Meet your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:35.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511407,515202}Yes. Tomorrow evening,\NMother's having a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515202,518247}I want to introduce you\Nas my fiancée there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:42.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518247,522251}Fiancée? You can't do that!\NI have no intentions to—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522251,524503}I'm still a junior high student!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:49.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524503,529592}You didn't hear the Chairman?\NI'm dating you with intentions to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:529592,531886}I've heard nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:55.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534472,535514}It's a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538267,540478}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540770,542480}Ah, she's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:06.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544565,546901}The news is all over the class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546901,548819}Is it true he proposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548819,551447}He's the son of the owner\Nof the Tomikoji Group!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:14.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552198,554116}How do all of you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.11,0:09:17.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554116,557161}Looks like the source of the news\Nis from over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:21.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557453,561874}Asuka Jr., have you seen it?\NIt's my greatest scoop! Hey, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561874,564668}Be quiet!\NAre you a show business reporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564668,566253}Don't get so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566253,568380}I said, be quiet, Saruwatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568380,569298}It's Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569298,571383}If you don't like Saruwatari,\Nhow about Sawagani?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571383,572927}What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572927,576263}That's jealousy.\NHey, Meimi, Miss Popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:45.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581602,585231}Meimi, I'm sorry to disturb you\Nwhen you're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:49.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585564,589443}Oh, Seira, you too! Don't be mean.\NIt's work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590027,593197}The job is for Miss Yumi Imamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593197,597910}She was a secretary for that\Nwoman entrepreneur, Madam Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:04.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597910,604917}But Madam Ranko has switched her mother's\Nheirloom necklace with a fake one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:07.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606377,607419}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:12.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607837,612508}President, this isn't the necklace\Nthat I left with you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:16.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613134,616053}What in the world\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:18.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616053,618889}Are you saying\NI replaced it with a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618889,622852}I know the real one.\NPlease give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622852,624520}Stop this right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.52,0:10:28.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624520,628732}If you don't trust me,\Nthen you don't have to work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628732,631318}Leave here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:35.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631318,635865}Yumi, who complained to Madam Ranko,\Nlost her job as secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635865,637700}What a terrible woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638742,641370}I understand.\NJust leave things to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:642079,644540}This is the fake necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:47.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644540,647877}It seems that Madam Ranko always\Nhas the real one on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:48.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647877,648878}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:53.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648878,653424}And your only chance is the party\Nthat's being held tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653424,655843}Wait, tomorrow's party?\NIs it…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:11:01.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656510,661182}Right. Madam Ranko's real name\Nis Ranko Tomikoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661182,663058}She's Ryutaro's mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:08.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664185,668814}The party tomorrow will include\Nforeign diplomats and other VIPs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668814,671859}so the security will be quite tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671859,673527}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:18.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673986,678991}I think the best way to get in\Nis to go to that party with Ryutaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:23.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679366,683370}Seira! Do you know what\Ngoing to that party means?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:26.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683370,686415}I won't! I'll get in there\Non my very own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687291,688834}Meimi.
Comment: 0,0:11:29.71,0:11:29.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:689710,689710}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:34.71,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:694715,694715}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:44.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701931,704600}Hey, Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:45.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704600,705768}Kick the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706769,708562}Sure. Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:06.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:722368,726747}"Tonight at the party hall, I'll be\Npicking up Madam Ranko's necklace."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727456,729458}A notice from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:11.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729458,731085}Hey, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731627,734004}What are you going\Nto do about this ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:18.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737925,738968}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:20.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738968,740261}Welcome home, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:22.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740261,742805}Welcome home. I'll get tea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:25.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742805,745474}Thanks, but, Mama…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:30.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746642,750688}It's beautiful!\NI've always wanted one like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:36.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751981,756652}Okay, you're getting sleepy.\NOne, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758946,762324}Wow! Papa, is this hypnotism?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762324,765369}But it's still in the research stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:49.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765369,769665}All right, when I count to three,\Nyou'll become a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:53.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769665,773127}One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:13:00.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778090,780509}I'd say it's quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:05.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780509,785055}When I count to three, you'll\Nreturn to normal. Three, two, one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786557,788934}What? I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:12.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788934,792104}Mother, you were\Na cat a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:14.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792104,794815}You used me as\Na guinea pig, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794815,797026}I'm sorry. Here's the pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:18.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797026,798944}You won't get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:21.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798944,801322}– Forgive me!\N– No, I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802948,804908}Shall we go? We're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:33.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812666,813834}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:42.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818547,822134}I knew you'd come to the party\Nwithout telling your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822509,823719}Ryutaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:47.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823719,827514}Shall we go?\NBut that dress just won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827514,829016}Old man, bring it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:50.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829016,830267}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830267,832686}What do you mean by "it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:57.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832686,837483}He'll bring the dress I selected\Nfor you, so please change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837483,838567}Young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843489,845032}Isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845991,849536}{\i1}Got no choice.\NI'll have to do as Seira said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:11.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849536,851997}{\i1}Plus, that's a nice dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:23.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:858212,863384}I don't need the security.\NAs you can see, I have the necklace on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:27.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:863717,867846}But St. Tail is able\Nto steal from anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:32.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868180,872101}As I've said, that is why\Nwe've hired our own security guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:37.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872101,877314}Also, to have you roam around\Ndressed like that is a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:41.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878065,881819}I don't mind if you do your security\Nbut do it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:44.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882111,884780}Please wait! I'm not finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888909,890244}Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:02.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900838,902172}Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:904925,906260}Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906260,907136}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:908262,909388}Haneoka…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:24.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918897,924445}{\i1}Haneoka. He really proposed to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936373,938750}That woman over there\Nis my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940669,942254}{\i1}That's the necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:42.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942254,942921}Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:43.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942921,943881}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943881,946675}Let's have one dance\Nbefore I introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:49.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946675,949344}No, thanks. I can't dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949344,950971}I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955058,957436}Meimi, you're quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957436,959646}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959646,962274}{\i1}Where's Madam Ranko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964151,965402}{\i1}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:09.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965402,969156}Ryutaro, I feel a bit ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969156,971325}Would you like a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:14.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971325,974244}No, don't worry. I'll be fine\Nwith a bit of fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977247,978624}Wonder if she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:34.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990761,994598}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999728,1000604}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003065,1004274}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006109,1008904}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023293,1026713}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028882,1031260}– What's this?\N– Where are the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.26,0:17:12.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031260,1032803}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037182,1038684}My necklace is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039393,1041186}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.47,0:17:23.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041478,1043647}She's appeared! Let's go!
